      <title>欧盟贸易负责人关闭时，特朗普征收震动全球贸易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/eu-trade-chiefs-close-ranks-as-trump-tariffs-jolt-global-trade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟贸易部长关闭了职务，并表示准备部署各种对策，包括对数字公司的潜在税收，以应对美国总统唐纳德·特朗普的广泛关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/eu-trade-chiefs-close-ranks-as-trump-tariffs-jolt-global-trade</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 14:04:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国告诉汽车制造商在特朗普关税达到打击后“我们有你的支持”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/uk-tells-automakers-we-have-your-back-after-trump-tariffs-blow</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯（Rachel Reeves）告诉英国汽车制造商，政府将在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）上周的关税使该行业陷入动荡之后，政府将支持他们。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/uk-tells-automakers-we-have-your-back-after-trump-tariffs-blow</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 13:59:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>VIX再次涌现，因为合同信号波动保持高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/vix-surges-again-as-contracts-signal-volatility-to-stay-high</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在隔夜尖峰高于60之后，CBOE波动率指数较高，并且期货曲线表明波动率可能会升高数月。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/vix-surges-again-as-contracts-signal-volatility-to-stay-high</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 13:57:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>华沙巴尔斯（Warsaw Bourse）暂停由于波动，高卷而导致的贸易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/warsaw-bourse-suspends-trade-due-to-volatility-high-volumes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，华沙证券交易所（Warsaw Stock Exchange）将在周一的一个多小时中暂停所有市场的贸易，理由是波动性和数量激增。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/warsaw-bourse-suspends-trade-due-to-volatility-high-volumes</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 13:54:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>S＆amp; p 500正在与熊市调情，因为关税达到了一切</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/s-p-500-is-heading-for-a-bear-market-as-tariffs-hit-everything</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统的贸易战争使美国自2022年以来首个熊市的悬崖上的股票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/s-p-500-is-heading-for-a-bear-market-as-tariffs-hit-everything</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 13:34:22 GMT</pubDate>
