    <item>
      <title>随着经济衰退风险的增长，摩根士丹利降低了银行业</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/morgan-stanley-downgrades-banking-sector-as-recession-risk-grows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根士丹利（Morgan Stanley）分析师对唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统的关税政策增加了经济衰退的风险，并威胁要延迟任何在交易中的复兴，因此摩根士丹利分析师对大型和中型银行的看法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/morgan-stanley-downgrades-banking-sector-as-recession-risk-grows</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 11:48:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲汽油价格在市场抛售后反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/european-gas-prices-extend-slump-as-market-rout-worsens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲天然气价格逆转了损失，在减少石油和全球股票的抛售后，损失了。]]></description>
