    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当关税战争升级时，中国股票“恐慌卖”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/chinese-stocks-plunge-amid-growing-fear-of-full-blown-trade-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着投资者为自己的影响，中国股价暴跌，主权收益率略低，因为投资者因世界上两个最大经济体之间的螺旋贸易冲突而陷入困境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/chinese-stocks-plunge-amid-growing-fear-of-full-blown-trade-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 01:30:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着债券的流失：市场包裹，股票很快消除了损失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/s-p-500-futures-slump-as-tariff-turmoil-deepens-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当华尔街交易员寻求底部的迹象之后，股票停止了销售踩踏事件，这使S＆amp; p 500在熊市的边缘放置了底部。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/s-p-500-futures-slump-as-tariff-turmoil-deepens-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 22:40:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国股票消灭4％的溃败，在野外交易中变为正面</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/us-stock-futures-tumble-with-trump-team-digging-in-on-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国的股票在公开场合的4％溃败中咆哮，技术股票领先，唐纳德·特朗普总统的贸易政策促进了全球金融市场的狂野回旋。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/us-stock-futures-tumble-with-trump-team-digging-in-on-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 22:04:42 GMT</pubDate>
